HEADWORD: Postcommissure
<hw>Post*com"mis*sure</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>post-</ets> + <ets>commisure</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld>
<def>A transverse commissure in the posterior part of the roof of the
third ventricle of the brain; the posterior cerebral commissure.</def>
<rj><au>B. G. Wilder.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

